name: Peter Parker
description: A high school student who balances life as a superhero with his everyday challenges.

name: Wade Wilson
description: An anti-hero with a twisted sense of humor and a knack for breaking the fourth wall.

name: Bruce Banner
description: A brilliant scientist who transforms into a giant green monster when angered.

name: Natasha Romanoff
description: A former spy and assassin who fights for justice.

name: Tony Stark
description: A genius billionaire who builds an advanced armored suit to fight crime.
